{
  "texts": [
    "However, three major challenges persist in GRN inference.",
    "First, learning such a complex mechanism from limited data points remains a challenge.",
    "Although single-cell data offers a large number of cells, most of them are not independent.",
    "Second, incorporating prior knowledge such as motif matching into non-linear models is challenging.",
    "Third, inferred GRN accuracy assessed by experimental data is only marginally better than random prediction 39."
  ]
}